EEPROM Mapping
FLW -> 0      
FRW -> 2
BLW -> 4
BRW -> 6

FLD -> 8
FRD -> 10
BLD -> 12
BRD -> 14

TRR -> 16
TRL -> 18
 
TLR -> 20
TLL -> 22

Control Mapping
1 -> F 
2 -> B
3 -> R
4 -> L
5 -> FR
6 -> FL
7 -> BR
8 -> BL
0 -> S

Meaning for Letter
T -> Trun
F -> Forward
R -> Right
L -> eft
B -> Backward
W -> Work
D -> Drive 
S -> Stop

TRR : Values form 0 -    63   TRL : Values form 192 - 255
TLR : Values form 64 -  127   TLL : Values form 128 - 191
FRW : Values form 0 -    40   FLW : Values form 128 - 168 
BRW : Values form 64 -  104   BLW : Values form 192 - 232
FRD : Values form 40 -   63   FLD : Values form 168 - 191 
BRD : Values form 104 - 127   BLD : Values form 232 - 255

RCWmin ->  Right Wheel Cloackwise Control Minimum
RCWmax ->  Right Wheel Cloackwise Control Maximum
RCCWmin -> Right Wheel Cloackwise Control Minimum
RCCWmax -> Right Wheel Cloackwise Control Maximum


LCWmin ->   Left Wheel Cloackwise Control Minimum
LCWmax ->   Left Wheel Cloackwise Control Maximum
LCCWmin ->  Left Wheel Cloackwise Control Minimum
LCCWmax ->  Left Wheel Cloackwise Control Maximum